OL,3,CReform MPs given 24-hour protection
OL,4,Cfollowing Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FReform UK MPs are being given round
OL,7,Fthe clock security protection, as
OL,8,Fpolice continue their murder
OL,9,Finvestigation into the death of Ann
OL,10,FWiddecombe.
OL,12,FThe veteran politician, a former Tory
OL,13,Fminister and later Reform
OL,14,Fspokesperson, was found dead at her
OL,15,Fhome in Haytor on Dartmoor at around
OL,16,F11.40am on Thursday after sustaining
OL,17,Fserious injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
