OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783835341
OL,3,CReform MPs given 24-hour protection
OL,4,Cfollowing Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FReform's MPs are now being given 24-
OL,7,Fhour security protection following
OL,8,FMiss Widdecombe's death, as first
OL,9,Freported by The Mail on Sunday.
OL,11,FThe security is being paid for by the
OL,12,Fparty and was offered for fear of
OL,13,Fsimilar attacks.
OL,15,FNigel Farage, the leader of Reform,
OL,16,Fvisited Devon on Saturday to lay a
OL,17,Fwreath for Miss Widdecombe and spoke
OL,18,Fto reporters about the case while he
OL,19,Fwas there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
