PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783835341
OL,3,CReform MPs given 24-hour protection
OL,4,Cfollowing Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FHe claimed Reform had gone through its
OL,7,Femails to check for patterns of abuse
OL,8,Fdirected at Ms Widdecombe, but had not
OL,9,Fbeen able to find anything.
OL,11,FOn Friday, he described Ms
OL,12,FWiddecombe's death as "a terrible
OL,13,Freflection on modern Britain".
OL,15,FHe added: "And I do fear that for
OL,16,Fanybody in public life, or especially
OL,17,Fthe political space, things have
OL,18,Fbecome even more dangerous to them."
